{"tid":1049353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國4月實施新例　登入色情網站須年齡驗證  英國人都要翻牆？","createTime":"2019-03-06T08:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T13:19:54.000Z","uid":236171,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d5b0704b1d1cb2b263564601cc87a16cf27cfdc5","tid":1049353,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T08:11:03.000Z","msg":"VPN 服務供應商可以做埋英國人生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180307/mobile/bknint-20180307094657800-0307_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180307%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20180307094657800-0307_17011_001.html&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhfkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=1ebbe39e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180307/mobile/bknint-20180307094657800-0307_17011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英國4月實施新例　登入色情網站須年齡驗證</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2018年03月07日(三) 09:46   <br />\n英國將要求所有色情網站用戶驗證年齡。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n英國由今年4月開始將會實施新規定，凡在國內登入色情網站的人都需要提供資料證明他們年滿18歲或以上，這個措施是政府《數碼經濟法案》的一部分，旨在保障未成年人和兒童不會接觸到不雅成人內容。 <br />\n<br />\n有經營多個色情網站的MindGeek公司表示，他們的年齡識別軟件「AgeID」自2015年已經在德國使用，軟件通過第三者年齡識別公司處理登記入成人網站用戶的資料。AgeID發言人表示，要識別登記者的年齡有多種方法，例如核對信用卡、護照、駕駛執照及手機內容等。不過，分析指這些文件仍然不確定是否符合法律規定。 <br />\n<br />\nAgeID表示，未來一經登記，用戶可以登入多個成人網站而不需要再每次登入。MindGeek公司則表示他們本身不會儲存任何數據，他們只是建立一個工具來符合英國的法例，既保障兒童不會接觸到成人內容，又確保成年人只要一次登記便可以安全及保有私隱地進入成人網站。不過這個軟件只適用於直接登入成人網站的公眾，而使用搜尋引擎或由社交網體進入色情內容的人士則不包括。 <br />\n<br />\n有關注團體表示，MindGeek公司稱不會儲存任何數據，那麼哪一家公司會儲存這些數據？而且登記的人將要公開他們的性取向。此外如果這些個人資料被黑客入侵盜取，英國的民眾將永遠不會再相信政府。 <br />\n<br />\n駐英國記者章怡報道"},{"pid":"c2e7cf1fd197e718b5619404cb54d857e64bb17a","tid":1049353,"uid":511,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T08:16:01.000Z","msg":"班廢老自己細個睇飽J飽，而家就唔准啲細嘅睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"195a5c0d607a6ab597452bf7dd5ab7bfcfd39b42","tid":1049353,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T08:16:33.000Z","msg":"1984元祖"},{"pid":"f7e69eeaae9c9327a9fcec59f012d1da09563ec3","tid":1049353,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T08:19:31.000Z","msg":"上 thisav 咪得囉"},{"pid":"b5e8c0bf15d3519c5523cddda2fee172eb86a162","tid":1049353,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T08:20:24.000Z","msg":"其實一早要提升認證方法<br />\n㩒個掣就入得，咪玩啦<br />\n但係其實佢應該為網絡審查鋪路<br />\n以後又推啲資訊網絡嘅licence<br />\n如果個網絡唔守就又罰又ban<br />\n好似Facebook嗰啲"},{"pid":"0b1a035206d87cc0d376d443b3091bbaefd6da54","tid":1049353,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T08:21:19.000Z","msg":"慘，丁都無得打。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287ff03e6dab6eaf9c090816931e70ae9fba0f14","tid":1049353,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T08:21:23.000Z","msg":"未滿十八歲者，請按此離開"},{"pid":"c87c7240ff6065ea78f09306e20c866f21f03068","tid":1049353,"uid":169310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T08:23:18.000Z","msg":"唔怪得之英國咁buy華爲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8806b75cd92cafc6f22d541f638f4dda03c77729","tid":1049353,"uid":236171,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T08:26:13.000Z","msg":"種少幾多棵樹，環保 L 又輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v4mJoKN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv4mJoKN.jpg&h=42f5f5e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7bcd6245597b0d326e3f17081e2b0165be6e99dd","tid":1049353,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7e69ee